WHO WE ARE


Squash Global is a multi-dimensional Digital Marketing Agency based out in Gurgaon comprising a team of Creative & Passionate young people. We provide solutions towards building future ready brands on digital platforms, through an integration of content, technology and media, using data backed tools and practices at the most competitive rates possible. Our bold imagination and always-ready-for-challenges help brands to shape the future, every day. At Squash, we cover all aspects of modern-day marketing & advertising solutions for the Next-Gen Marketers'.

We call ourselves Creative Scientists and like most Scientist, we can be pretty crazy to challenge the standard market norms. Our team has creative dreamers and rational thinkers who believe in delivering solutions that are designed with the perfect balance between Creativity and Strategy. We put our heart and soul to every projects we work on. Think of us like an extension of your marketing team, sharing the same dreams and same goals.Â
